Mirrorselect provides a nice interface to select the mirrors you want. Just navigate to the mirrors of choice and press spacebar to select one or more mirrors.
{{emerge|app-portage/mirrorselect}}

Find Gentoo mirror (set [[SYNC|SYNC variable]]):
{{Cmd|mirrorselect -i -o >> /etc/make.conf}}

Find Gentoo rsync server (set [[GENTOO_MIRRORS|GENTOO_MIRRORS variable]]):
{{Cmd|mirrorselect -i -r -o >> /etc/make.conf}}

Find 3 fastest servers by downloading 100K from each:
{{Cmd|mirrorselect -s3 -b10 -o -D >> /etc/make.conf}}
